data.description: Price Improvement! LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION! Come be a part of the vibrant and highly sought-after Deer Creek Community in Palmer Ranch! Set in the well-established neighborhood of over 500 custom-built homes you'll find this beautifully maintained community provides 24/7 guarded gate access, lush tropical flora, 17 lakes, and majestic oaks lining the streets that tell stories of Old Florida Natural Wildlife. Take a stroll or bike ride and enjoy the beauty of this distinguished community and don't be surprised if you spot a Bald Eagle along the way. This Single Family Gem is located in the Villas at Deer Creek where residents benefit from a private community pool and neighborhood activities for social gatherings. With over 2000 sq ft of living space, this split plan features 2 bedrooms, 2 baths PLUS a bonus room that offers high cathedral ceilings, a vast living area, spacious kitchen with an eat-in dining area, or a separate formal dining area. Off the living area is the enclosed Florida room leading to the paved and screened-in lanai where you can enjoy morning sunrises and quiet nights in the privacy of the thriving preserve in your backyard. The laundry is conveniently located just off the kitchen before you enter into the 2 car garage. This home features 2018 Stainless Steel Appliances, 2021 AC, 2020 Water Heater. Come create your vision and make this home yours! With some TLC the possibilities are endless. Centrally located within a short drive to everything you need from Home Depot, Kohls, Costco, Wal Mart Super Center, Target, AMC Movie Theatre, Super Markets, and a wide range of restaurants and specialty shops you won't need to travel far for your shopping needs. Enjoy the proximity to several Golf Courses, local YMCA, Serendipity Tennis Complex, the Legacy Trail, Potter Park where you can enjoy nature trails, tennis, basketball, playgrounds and picnic tables. A short distance to Florida's #1 World Renowned Siesta Key Beaches! Discover the blend of modern comfort and timeless charm that this home offers. This is truly living the Florida Lifestyle!
